00:08:11.579 --> 00:08:17.579
We cannot go wrong by imitating Jesus in any way possible.

00:08:17.579 --> 00:08:22.579
Recall that 1 Peter 2 verse 21 says,

00:08:22.579 --> 00:08:27.579
